a three-hitter in the first game, then watched as Christ College's Lisa Merenda 
picked up a win of her own in the nightcap, as the teams split an NAIA District 
3 doubleheader at Cal Lutheran. 
</P>
<P>
In the opener, Kim White homered, tripled and drove in two runs. But she then 
lost her 11-game hitting streak to Merenda in the second game. 
</P>
