<TEXT>
<P>
New address: Frank B. Hall &amp; Co. Inc., one of the nation's largest 
insurance brokerage firms, has moved its West Coast regional office to Costa 
Mesa from downtown Los Angeles "because Orange County is fast becoming an 
important international center for business and commerce within the Pacific 
Rim," said Ron Jackson, chief executive for the Costa Mesa office. The new 
regional office is in the Imperial Bank building near South Coast Plaza. 
</P>
